Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:08.86,Tea on Rice,Sign 0004,0004,0001,0018,,{\an8}{\fad(689,1)}Azure Messenger Bomb Threat Incident \N First Investigation Meeting \N Armed Detective Agency Conference Room
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.88,0:00:06.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,At present, we have an unidentified \Ncriminal organization
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.72,0:00:08.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,threatening to detonate a large \Nbomb in a metropolitan area
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:12.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,and launch a smear campaign \Nagainst the Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:15.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Yosano,0000,0000,0000,,I know the Agency's between \Na rock and a hard place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.71,0:00:18.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Yosano,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us more about the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:22.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,This is the message left \Nbehind by the perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:23.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I'll read it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:28.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,"Greetings, I hope your \Nagency is faring well."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.78,0:00:32.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,"Forgive my impudence, but I have placed a bomb"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:36.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,"capable of causing mass destruction in a \Ncertain location here in Yokohama City."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:39.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,"To secure the citizens' safety,"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:44.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,"I request that you locate and disarm \Nthe bomb at your earliest convenience."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.59,0:00:46.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,"You have until sundown."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.39,0:00:48.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,"I have faith in your abilities."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:50.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,"Respectfully, the Azure Messenger."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:53.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,Who could the Azure Messenger be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:00:55.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know as of yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:58.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Yosano,0000,0000,0000,,So it's all rigged so that \Nif the bomb detonates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.45,0:01:02.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Yosano,0000,0000,0000,,word of the Agency's failure \Nwill spread like wildfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:06.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Yosano,0000,0000,0000,,The Agency can weather sticks and stones,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:09.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Yosano,0000,0000,0000,,but this type of attack would hit us hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.23,0:01:14.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Since yesterday, the office staff have \Nbeen searching for plausible locations,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:16.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,but there are too many possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:17.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Kenji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.56,0:01:20.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Kenji,0000,0000,0000,,Are we still unable to reach Rampo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.77,0:01:23.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the case in Kyuushuu \Nis coming to a head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:27.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I've requested he contact us as \Nsoon as the criminal is caught, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.63,0:01:29.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,Any further information \Nfrom that taxi driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:32.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,He denies any knowledge of the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.30,0:01:36.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't have it in him \Nto blow up Yokohama itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.79,0:01:38.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:44.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,This case is a cowardly act using information\N to attack the Armed Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:46.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,We have two objectives:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.61,0:01:48.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,uncover the Azure Messenger, the instigator,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:50.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,and disarm the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:54.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,The bomb takes priority due \Nto its time-sensitive nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.85,0:01:58.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,If we cannot find the \Nbomb and lives are lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:00.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,we no longer have the right to call \Nourselves a detective agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.09,0:02:06.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,Think of this mission as a fight for \Nthe Agency's existence and pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:17.52,Stray Dogs - Italics,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,What time do you think\N it is, idiot four-eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:19.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one I know \Nwho's still sleeping at 9:00 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:23.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can find the Azure Messenger,\N the one who sent us that message?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:29.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you calling because you had \Nsomething else you wanted to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:31.70,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,So you know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:34.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,I only know what I actually know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.74,0:02:37.24,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask you about tracing \Nthe bomb-building equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:39.06,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you the shipping manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:40.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:41.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,Things are looking up for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:44.76,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the small talk and get cracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:45.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:48.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,This is to save lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:51.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You may be regularly indulging \Nin illicit activities,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,but you should make yourself useful \Nto society sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:54.97,Stray Dogs - Italics,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,Get off your high horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:57.45,Stray Dogs - Italics,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,You're not my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:03.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:07.12,Stray Dogs Ep Title,Sign 0304,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(345,18)}Episode 7 \N Love for the Disease Called Ideals
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:06.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I can never be your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:10.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:13.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,The Agency seemed hectic \Ndue to the bomb threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:16.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-sama seemed very busy, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:20.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-kun is a workhorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:23.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he always spends two \Nhours before going to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,reviewing and revising his notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:26.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt I could stand doing \Nthat for two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:29.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's got some solider ants \Nworking for him in his brain—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:32.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I didn't know you \Nwere here, Kunikida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,How could you ditch the \Nmeeting during an emergency
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:37.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,and go on a fancy afternoon date?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Are you jealous of the fancy date?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:40.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:41.98,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,So he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:45.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,She's a victim who was nearly killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:49.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Ensuring her safety and tending \Nto her psychological well-being
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:52.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,is an important and urgent duty \Nfor the Agency, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:58.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you, the poster child for sloth and\N irresponsibility, a good fit for the task?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:01.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, given her good looks,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I'd assume she has a boyfriend at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:06.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, they broke up recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:08.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, Kunikida-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:09.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I say you can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:10.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Dazai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:15.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I came here because you skipped \Nout on the morning meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:17.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,and I need to tell you what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:19.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:22.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The goal of the Azure Messenger\N who set the bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:24.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,is to crush the Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:26.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:31.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure an outsider like \Nme should be hearing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:32.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:34.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Sasaki-san's a person of \Ninterest in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:35.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,There's no issue here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:36.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:40.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Sasaki-san, what's the class you \Nteach at the university again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:41.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,Social psychology.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:43.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:46.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to hear what you \Nthink about this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:51.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,About the Azure Messenger...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:54.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,It may have something to \Ndo with the Azure King
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:57.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,in the notorious Azure \NFlag Terrorist incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:04:59.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,So you think that, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:02.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,It could very well be the \NAzure King himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:06.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that he blew himself up after \Nbeing cornered by the police, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,it's possible he faked his death
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,and is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:13.09,Stray Dogs - Italics,AK,0000,0000,0000,,This world is incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:14.98,Stray Dogs - Italics,AK,0000,0000,0000,,One may grieve or pray,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.72,Stray Dogs - Italics,AK,0000,0000,0000,,but people still die from \Naccidental circumstance,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:19.92,Stray Dogs - Italics,AK,0000,0000,0000,,and evil goes unpunished to \Nflourish freely in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:22.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,A former official,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:26.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,the Azure King set off a bomb in a \Ngovernment facility and issued a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:30.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,His targets included killers whose cases were \Ndropped due to incompetent prosecutors,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:35.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,as well as diet members who were engaged in \Npolitical corruption on a global scale...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:36.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,All dangerous criminals untouchable by law.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:40.74,Stray Dogs - Italics,AK,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall desire the ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:42.64,Stray Dogs - Italics,AK,0000,0000,0000,,It will be built not by \Nthe divine hand of God
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:45.64,Stray Dogs - Italics,AK,0000,0000,0000,,but by our own bloodied fingers...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:51.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,But if the Azure King is alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:54.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,why would he attack the Agency like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:55.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:58.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the one who backed the \NAzure King into a corner
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:01.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,is Kunikida-kun, who located his hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:02.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:05.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-kun is the target \Nof vengeance here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:10.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,The terrorist's death was confirmed by the \Nmilitary police after forensic analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:12.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:13.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Either way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:16.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,you should stay on your guard \Nuntil you figure out who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.09,0:06:19.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to hide Sasaki-san \Nsomewhere safe, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:21.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,That I will not allow, Dazai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:22.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:25.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can keep a lady in your room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:27.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,in the name of personal safety?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:31.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,And day and night, do such \Nand such unthinkable things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:32.63,Stray Dogs - Top,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like what you're imagining\N is happening, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:32.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Shame on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:33.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:35.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,When I first let her stay,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:37.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I slept in an adjoining room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:39.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,and didn't lay a finger on her, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:42.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I knew you misunderstood,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:45.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,but I thought it was funny \Nso I didn't correct you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:48.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I really wonder why these two are partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:55.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-kun seems to like Sasaki-san a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:57.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Sasaki-san, what type of man do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:06:59.73,Stray Dogs - Default,Nabuko,0000,0000,0000,,T-Type?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:06.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Nabuko,0000,0000,0000,,It would be presumptuous of me to \Neven have such a thing in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:11.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Nabuko,0000,0000,0000,,But... I do think it is wonderful when \Na man strongly believes in an ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Nabuko,0000,0000,0000,,and pours his heart and soul into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:16.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's totally Kunikida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, the two of you can pick up the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:20.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dazai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:22.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-Don't go making assumptions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:25.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-kun, you're an open book.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:26.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:29.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,He may be a bit twisted,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:33.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,but as you can see, he is a high-minded \Nindividual who lives and breathes for his ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:36.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Although, perhaps for that reason, \Nhis ideal woman is a bit of a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.27,ideal,Sign 0738,0001,0001,0083,,{\an8}Ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:38.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard, not again! When did you—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:43.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:46.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:47.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,This goes too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:53.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-san's crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.62,Typewriter Text Sign - small for phone msg,Sign 0759,0000,0000,0000,,From: Haruno Kirako \N Subject: Received Word from Rampo-san \N Atsushi-kun, \N We heard back from Rampo-san! \NHis case is finished, so he has time to help us. \N Haruno Kirako
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:01.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,We finally heard from Rampo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:06.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,{Eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:15.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,So we know where the bomb is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:23.60,Typewriter Text Sign - small for phone msg,Sign 0819,0040,0001,0108,,{\an8}{\fad(399,1)}Edogawa \NRampo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:19.10,Stray Dogs - Italics,Rampo,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was hoping to sightsee in Kyuushuu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:21.86,Stray Dogs - Italics,Rampo,0000,0000,0000,,and eat a hot springs egg now \Nthat I solved my case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:23.59,Stray Dogs - Italics,Rampo,0000,0000,0000,,You all disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:27.25,Stray Dogs - Italics,Rampo,0000,0000,0000,,You can't conduct a single \Ninvestigation properly without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We only have until sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:30.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell us the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:32.32,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,A department store?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.17,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,A school?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.47,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Or a train station?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:37.58,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Any one of these could produce \Ncasualties in the hundreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.71,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:40.90,Stray Dogs - Italics,Rampo,0000,0000,0000,,The fishing tackle store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:41.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:44.98,Stray Dogs - Italics,Rampo,0000,0000,0000,,The bomb was set in a fishing \Ntackle store in Negishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:47.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Rampo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:53.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,But why a fishing tackle store?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:54.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have a map?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:56.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Behind the seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:58.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Page 97.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:09:01.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Page 97, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:05.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The terrorist's target is \Nthe petrochemical complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:06.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why I didn't realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:11.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Yokohama is one of Japan's major port towns.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:16.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Here, there are many large facilities \Nthat store oil and gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:21.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,If an explosion were to occur close enough \Nto ignite the storage tanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:25.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,the entire port will be \Nengulfed in flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:30.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,However, infiltrating a \Nfacility of that nature
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:33.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,will require getting past \Npretty good security.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:36.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The easiest approach would \Nbe to put a bomb in a car,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:39.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,and leave the car near \None of the facilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:43.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,So, considering the effective range of \Na bomb that can be loaded into a car...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:47.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,That fishing tackle store is the one \Nplace that checks all the boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:05.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The military police's bomb disposal \Nsquad has found the bomb,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:07.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,but the bomb can't be moved \Ndue to the timer device.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:10.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,They say it'll be difficult \Nto disarm it by sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:13.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We're having the nearby residents evacuate,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:15.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,but we're not sure there's enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:16.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:21.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,However, the bomb's set to deactivate\Nif we can transmit a stop signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:23.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:28.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:29.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,A phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:30.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:31.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:33.26,Stray Dogs - Italics,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Four-Eyes, is now a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:34.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Rokuzou?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:34.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:35.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:38.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I feel we're causing a traffic jam...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:42.59,Stray Dogs - Italics,Rampo,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Atsushi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:43.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Rampo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:44.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:45.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:45.53,Stray Dogs - Italics,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:46.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,President?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:47.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:49.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What? The military police's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:51.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Set a thief to catch a thief, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:53.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:55.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:55.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:56.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:56.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:58.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:11:00.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:01.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I got a call from Rokuzou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:08.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Someone recently ordered a \Ntransmitter and other equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,to be delivered to a former \Ndefense force facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:12.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Rampo-san reached a similar conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:13.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,That settles it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:16.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,My call was from the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:19.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,He was informed by the military \Npolice that the driver has died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:20.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:24.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought he was in the military \Npolice's isolation ward for protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:27.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,He died after suddenly collapsing \Nin pain in his cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:28.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The cause of death is unknown,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:34.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,but the numbers "00" were \Nmarked on his palm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:36.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Numbers on his palm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:37.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:40.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:48.22,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 1146,0444,0001,0010,,{\an8}Former Defense\N Force Facility
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:48.22,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 1147,0440,0001,0068,,{\an8}T-20 Minutes\N Until Detonation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:51.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Doppo Poet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:11:59.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Flash Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:04.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,We're at the right place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you, go upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Find the transmitter and \Nsend the stop signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:16.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:21.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your number.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:24.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,How've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:27.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:30.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you have a great number.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:34.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:38.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,You sniffed out the place just \Nlike your reputation predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:40.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,The Armed Detective Agency's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:42.73,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,Very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,The sun's setting...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:50.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Can you figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:53.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:53.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:57.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You have to insert the release \Nkey here and turn it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.68,0:12:59.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:00.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:02.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Giant,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:06.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, we've got quite a heavy hitter here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:14.30,Stray Dogs - Italics,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,This one's ability can \Nperform remote attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:16.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,What's your number now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Number?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:24.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Gold,0000,0000,0000,,My ability cannot be evaded, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:26.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Gold,0000,0000,0000,,I can send people who have numbers
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:29.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Gold,0000,0000,0000,,in any direction I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:32.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Gold,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they're on the \Nother side of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:35.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Gold,0000,0000,0000,,And once their number becomes zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.42,0:13:37.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Gold,0000,0000,0000,,they'll die in agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:40.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Gold,0000,0000,0000,,None can escape that fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:41.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Gold,0000,0000,0000,,None...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:43.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Gold,0000,0000,0000,,None...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:44.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Gold,0000,0000,0000,,No one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:47.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the leader of this group?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:50.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,Your group poses a greater obstacle \Nthan the Mafia, to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:53.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,But the Armed Detective \NAgency is now finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:55.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:58.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,It's the release key to stop the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:01.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,Without it, you can't stop the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:04.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:07.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it... here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:10.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,Now, there is no hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:13.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,It's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,It's over, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:16.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:23.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Atsushi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:29.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You have really strong arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:32.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You should have gone into \Nthe porter business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:46.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:47.49,sign_31821_418_Wire_Gun,Sign 1447,0001,0270,0046,,{\an8}{\fad(1,187)}Wire Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:48.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:54.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you can pull \Nthe same trick twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:57.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:14:58.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:06.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be the next one \Nto give me a number?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:10.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:12.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Blond,0000,0000,0000,,Why has no number marked you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:16.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, your ability will \Nno longer have any effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:20.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you should really have your partner \Nswitch careers and be a porter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:27.98,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,The weight difference doesn't \Nseem to faze him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:30.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:33.57,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Their partnership is amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:35.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:37.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-san, the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:38.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,He broke it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:39.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:41.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about the bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:42.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:43.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:46.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Doppo Poet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.00,sign_31821_418_Wire_Gun - Copy DARK,Sign,0358,0001,0143,,{\fad(1,96)}Release Key
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Release key.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:52.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,My ability allows me to recreate \Nanything if I have laid eyes on it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:55.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,and understood its form and function.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:09.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,However, the object's size is \Nlimited to that of a pocketbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:09.69,ideal,Sign 1609,0262,0001,0133,,Ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:15.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,So your notebook is really a tool \Nthat brings your ideals into reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:27.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're visiting the graves of \Nthose who have lost their lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:29.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:34.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,When I first caused casualties during a job,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:36.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I cried so much I couldn't get up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:37.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,and I took time off from work without leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:40.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,But now, I don't even shed a tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:45.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I just choose to visit their graves in \Nexchange, or that's how I think of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:51.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,Will the dead by comforted by tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:54.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt they'd be comforted \Nor redeemed by tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:58.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,After all, their time stopped \Nat the moment of their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:03.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,I confess I told a lie earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:07.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,My significant other and I \Nparted ways because he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:08.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:10.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,What you said is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:14.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,Time no longer has meaning for the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:16.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I may do for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:17.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,he cannot rejoice in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:19.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,nor smile because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:24.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my composure without meaning to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:27.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,I have something I must attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:28.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:32.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:38.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.48,0:17:40.63,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.63,0:17:42.43,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I need you for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:45.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want here, of all places?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:52.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It's a survey of Yokohama we found\N on a computer in their hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:56.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Surprisingly, it concludes that eradicating \Nthe Agency is the first priority
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:59.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,in order to take control of Yokohama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:02.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,And not the Port Mafia, \Nwho control the underworld?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:06.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,They were being manipulated \Nby false information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:08.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,So there's another mastermind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:13.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I've sent an email to the \None I believe is truly behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:16.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I said I have proof that the person \Nis the one truly responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:19.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That person should be here any moment now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:30.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:32.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one, Rokuzou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:34.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:36.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,So it hasn't started yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:38.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:41.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You took a peek at my email by hacking \Ninto my account, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:43.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,So it's not really you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:46.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to take a look at the \None who's actually responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:49.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,So it's really, really not you, right—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:49.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:58.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the Azure Messenger,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:00.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Sasaki Nobuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:02.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:06.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt this is the first time \Nyou used your intelligence
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:08.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,to execute a crime, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:10.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,He was a man who lived for his ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.49,0:19:14.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,He was pure in his intentions \Nto seek out the world of crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:17.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,and that is why he got blood on his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:21.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to grant his desire \Nand make his ideals come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:23.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Your significant other, the Azure King,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:27.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,was an idealist who wanted to prosecute \Ncriminals who could not be judged by law
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:29.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,through illegal means.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:30.98,Typewriter Text Sign - small for phone msg,Sign 1929,0338,0001,0030,,{\an8}Enhance\N Reflection
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:31.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,This incident was meant \Nto carry on his work...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:33.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Lower your gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:34.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,What good will this accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:36.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:40.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,You resemble him in a way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:43.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Your plan was very sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:46.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Without committing a single \Ncrime of your own,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:48.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,you set up the Agency to take the fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:51.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,and you destroyed both the kidnapper and \Nthe criminal organization behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:55.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,But you yourself have no \Nconvictions or ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:57.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You're just being swept along by the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just tired, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:04.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be released from all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:09.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,Will you shoot me, Dazai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:13.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,But I've lowered my gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to shoot me now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:17.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be excessive use of force.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.29,0:20:20.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Nobuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-san's watching us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:22.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:23.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I can't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:26.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:42.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,The Azure King killed my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:45.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Roku,0000,0000,0000,,Good riddance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:51.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:53.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it have to end this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:55.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,What went wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:57.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Who was wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:20:58.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,No one was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:00.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,This was the only possible outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:02.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:04.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You could've saved her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:07.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying this is justice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:09.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Justice is a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:11.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It can be used to cause harm,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:14.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,but it cannot protect or save others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:18.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What killed Sasaki-san was, in the end, \Nthe justice of the Azure King
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:20.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,and of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:24.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:27.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,as long as you pursue your ideals,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.71,0:21:31.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,the flames that burned in the Azure King \Nwill one day take root in you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:33.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,and raze everything around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:34.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Still!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.65,0:21:36.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I'll still push on until I push past it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:39.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate my ideals!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:23:09.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.59,0:23:12.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Yosano,0000,0000,0000,,Atsushi, aren't you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.98,0:23:14.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,No, not in the slightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.61,0:23:16.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I am in good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.02,0:23:18.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Yosano,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Um, about your "treatment," Dr. Yosano.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.49,0:23:22.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,How does it work, specifically?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:23.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Yosano,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.72,0:23:26.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Yosano,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you ask Tanizaki since \Nhe was treated by me before?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:29.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but Tanizaki-san just shivers in fear
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:31.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,and won't tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.77,0:23:34.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Bungo Stray Dogs, Episode 8:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.79,0:23:36.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Yosano Akiko,0000,0000,0000,,Teaching Them To Kill; Then To Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:36.62,Stray Dogs Next ep title,Yosano Akiko,0072,0001,0111,,Episode 8 \NTeaching Them To Kill; Then To Die
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:39.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Yosano,0000,0000,0000,,Ability: Thou Shalt Not Die.
